{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint\/removecoordinatesinrange:"]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeCoordinatesInRange:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSRange","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@_NSRange"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"range"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"range","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The range of vertices to remove. The ","type":"text"},{"code":"location","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" field indicates","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the first vertex you are removing, with ","type":"text"},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being the first vertex, ","type":"text"},{"code":"1","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"being the second vertex, and so on. The ","type":"text"},{"code":"length","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" field indicates the number"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of vertices to remove."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the shape is currently visible on the map as an annotation, it is redrawn"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"immediately. If the shape is part of an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object, you must"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"explicitly set the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/shape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" property in order for any style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layers that use the source to be redrawn."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" extends beyond the shape’s "},{"code":"coordinates","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"NSRangeException","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is raised."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes the vertices at the given range from the shape."}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint\/removeCoordinatesInRange:"},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPoint(im)removeCoordinatesInRange:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeCoordinatesInRange:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"removeCoordinatesInRange:","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeCoordinatesInRange:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"title":"MLNShape","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"typ